    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who values utility over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car runs reliably, there are visible signs of age including minor scratches, some fading in the paint, and wear on the interior upholstery. It has been well-maintained mechanically with regular oil changes, but expect the typical quirks associated with a car of this age. It's a solid, functional choice for getting from A to B without the high price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This car is in honest, fair condition and is ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some expected signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a solid, functional vehicle at a great price. It's a practical find that's perfect for commuting or as a first car\u2014come see the value for yourself!",
      "price": 24500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading paint on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits clear signs of wear, including a small tear in the driver's seat upholstery and some staining on the floor mats. Mechanically, it has been maintained to ensure it remains roadworthy, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. It is a solid, honest car that will get you where you need to go without any pretense.",
      "price": 23400.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its consistent maintenance history and robust performance capabilities. This specimen offers an exceptional balance of aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity, ensuring a refined experience for its next owner. Vetted for quality and prepared to our exacting standards, this automobile represents a superior investment for those seeking dependable luxury and proven endurance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me. It runs like a dream and is ready to hit the road for many more adventures. Whether you're cruising around town or headed on a weekend getaway, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you can just hop in and enjoy. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this 2004 BMW M3, a quintessential example of the E46 platform. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a high-redline performance profile. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior torque vectoring. This vehicle has undergone critical preventive maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive valve shim adjustment. The suspension is taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry for precise lateral grip. While showing minor patina indicative of its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Regularly serviced. Interior is well-kept. Minor exterior scuffs. Drives smooth.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a testament to responsible ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only minor road peppering consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and crisp; the premium upholstery is supple, showing only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side. Mechanically, it is in excellent health with a documented service history, recent fluid flushes, and tires with significant tread remaining. All electronics, including the infotainment system and safety suites, function perfectly. It is a reliable, high-performing car that balances sophistication with everyday dependability.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
